↓  
Update Record  
↓  
Confirmation message

Example confirmation:

Updated rub_payment_bank_name_ru → rub_test ✅

---

# Airtable Update Logic

1. Search Records (no formula)

Max records: 50

2. Filter:

key = config_key

3. Update Record:

Record ID = SearchRecord.id  
value = new_value

This prevents accidental creation of new rows.

---

# Telegram Module Notes

Confirmation message uses:

Chat ID: message.chat.id  
Text: Updated {{config_key}} → {{config_value}} ✅

Important:

Disable **Advanced Settings** unless using buttons.  
Otherwise Make may send an empty keyboard and cause an error.

